---
title: Ras El Hanout Beef Bowl with Rice Pilaf & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Roll up for our latest take on a pilaf – a Moroccan version with ras el hanout! This adventurous spice blend gives the beef an abundance of flavour while the garnishes of roasted almonds, mint and lemon yoghurt round out the meal perfectly.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ras-el-hanout-beef-bowl-26f62ff3.jpg
